In Lieu of Gifts

There is no better gift than the honor of your presence and fervent prayers,

But if you intend to send us a gift,

Please know that we will reside in Singapore.

Request from the Couple

Though we would love to celebrate with your entire family,

Let the kids retire early for the night and come celebrate with us in an adults-only affair.

Oh Snap!
